<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَدْ قِيلَ:</span> الْمِحَالُ: الْحِيلَةُ؛ وَمِنْ هَذَا قَوْلُ ذِي الرُّمَّةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وَلَبَّسَ بَيْنَ أَقْوَامٍ وَكُلٌّ ... أَعَدَّ لَهُ الشغارب والمحالا)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">يَعْنِي:</span> الكيد وَالْمَكْر.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سُورَة الرَّعْد من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(١٤)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(١٦)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>